Main Hand: Cone of the Mystics (5 AC, 5 INT/WIS, 50 Mana)<br>
Legs: Apothic/Velious Leggings (Stats vary)<br>
<br>
<br>
The Girdle goes for like 2k on my server I think, and the Cone of Mystics maybe 1k. Apothic Legs are pretty good, and they seem to be a pretty common Apothic drop, if you have a chance to go to PoH. Velious Quest Legs (or PoG) are pretty good Legs if you have a shot at getting any of those. I don't really know of a better Wrist item to suggest.. maybe Velium Blue Diamond Bracelet? They are 30 Mana, 9 SVR All, if I remember correctly.<br>
<br>
Overall your gear doesn't seem that bad for a level 40. What upgrades you go with would depend on how your future will look. Are you going to join a guild, or go to 60 guildless? Do you plan on attending public raids? Or just exping? Those would play big factors on your future gear selection.<br>
